.TP
.B libs/python/drivers/
Driver-interface adapters for graphs.
.TP
.B libs/python/graph/
Graph execution engine.
.TP
.B libs/python/persistence/
Document store for graphs and sessions.
.TP
.B man/
Manual pages (you are here).
.SH INFRASTRUCTURE
.TP
.B Ollama
Local LLM server on port 1500. Runs models like Llama, Mistral, CodeLlama.
.TP
.B Whisper
OpenAI's speech recognition, loaded directly via Python.
.TP
.B PostgreSQL
Optional persistence for sessions and documents.
.TP
.B Redis
Optional caching layer.
